# Page Rhythm (Mandatory)

Full contract: [Page-Rhythm-Standard.md](../../docs/02_FLUTTER_MIGRATION/Page-Rhythm-Standard.md)  
Reference: `flutter_app/lib/features/home/presentation/pages/home_page_part_01.dart`

## When editing presentation pages

1. Set `VitPageContent(rhythm: VitPageRhythm.<tier>)` — tab roots use **`compact`**.
2. Put each **major section** as a **direct child** of `VitPageContent` — not one `_FooBody` `Column`.
3. Do **not** add `SizedBox(height: AppSpacing.sectionGap|x1|x2|x3|x4|x5|…)` between `VitPageContent` children — use `pageRhythm*SectionGap`, `pageRhythm*InnerGap`, `rowGap`, or `pageRhythmCompactInnerGap`.
4. Do **not** use `customGap: AppSpacing.x*` or compound `x3±` / `x4±` / `x* + digit` in rhythm `SizedBox` — use `VitPageRhythm` tiers and `pageRhythm*` tokens.
5. Do **not** nest `VitPageContent` only for spacing — flatten siblings.
6. Section headers: `VitSectionHeader(bottomGap: …)` or `pageRhythm*InnerGap` after title.
7. Prefer `pageRhythm*SectionGap` / `pageRhythm*InnerGap` over module `*SectionGap` for page rhythm.

## Tiers

| Role | Tier |
| --- | --- |
| Bottom-nav tab root (Home, Markets, Trade, Wallet, Profile) | `compact` |
| Standard scroll / settings / detail | `standard` |
| Forms / wizard / KYC / bottom sheets | `form` |
| Hero / onboarding (icon→title blocks only) | `relaxed` |
| Chart / terminal | `flush` |

## Verify before batch complete

```bash
cd flutter_app
dart run tool/page_rhythm_audit.dart --check
flutter test test/quality/page_rhythm_guardrail_test.dart --reporter=compact
```

Exception comment: `// page-rhythm: allow-single-child` for documented single-child shells.
